		{
			dependencies: ["5A5B0010CCDD0010"]
			description: ["The Twilight Lich commands a tall Lich Tower that generates in snow-covered forest clearings. Unlike the Naga, the Lich cannot be damaged until all four Lich Shields orbiting it are destroyed — strike the shields first while staying mobile to avoid the Lich's ranged attacks. After the shields break, the Lich enters aggressive phase and summons undead followers. The Lich Trophy it drops is required for the HV Machine Hull recipe alongside Stainless Steel. The Trophy cannot be substituted; there is no alternative source."]
