		{
			dependencies: ["8C8D0004EEFF0004"]
			description: ["Titanium is smelted from Rutile ore or Ilmenite ore in the EBF at 1941K — well within your Kanthal Coils' 2700K range. Process Rutile Ore through the Macerator to obtain Rutile Dust, then feed to the EBF. Titanium Ingots are required for Titanium Plates, which are a prerequisite for the EV Machine Hull and the AE2 ME Controller. Titanium is also the highest-tier structural metal in this progression tier — EV machines, the ME network, and the Ur-Ghast Trophy gate all converge on it."]
