		}
		{
			dependencies: ["8C8D0008EEFF0008"]
			description: ["Titanium Plates are produced by running Titanium Ingots through the Bender. They are a structural requirement for the EV Machine Hull and for the ME Controller that gates Applied Energistics 2 digital storage. Begin converting all Titanium output to Plates immediately — the AE2 network is one of the most material-intensive constructions in the EV tier and Titanium Plates are consumed across its entire component chain. Produce a reserve of at least 32 before beginning EV machine construction."]
