				"8C8D000AEEFF000A"
			]
			description: ["The Ur-Ghast is a massive flying creature that patrols the Dark Tower — a towering fortress found in the Dark Forest. It requires Ur-Ghast Tears (thrown by the boss mid-fight) to be redirected back at it for damage; conventional attacks do little until this mechanic is resolved. Its Trophy is required for the EV Machine Hull recipe, alongside Titanium Plates. Applied Energistics 2's ME Controller additionally requires Terrasteel Plates from the Botania endgame — two separate progression threads must converge at Extreme Voltage. Prepare for both."]
